headline: Cognex: Expansion Into The Logistics Market May Grow Profitability Into 2026
summary: Cognex Q3 2025 revenues and adjusted EBITDA YoY rise were driven by new AI-powered logistics products and factory automation. Read why CGNX stock is a Hold.
